280 to 310 grams...

LEOPOLD
Average female heart- weight?

Leopold climbs down. In his hand we notice a switch-thin cane.

YOUNG VICTOR
230 to 280 grams, Father-

LEOPOLD
Why would you say that is- the difference of mass in the female heart? Depth of emotions, a tendency towards the melancholic?

YOUNG VICTOR
Mass- volume of blood, Father. Muscular irrigation.

LEOPOLD
Quite. There is no spiritual function to tissue, Victor-- no emotion to a muscle-Now- describe the main function of the tricuspid valve.

