I'm sure you will. Ivory does not bleed, Victor. Flesh does- by the time you remember a fact- your patient could be dead. You understand?
(beat)
The tricuspid valve prevents reflux of blood into the vena cava.

He raises the cane. Young Victor extends his hands-

